title: HON HVL531
description: Featuring a black mesh back, a mesh fabric upholstered seat and a dynamic back design, the basyx® by HON VL531 presents quite a first impression. Then when you sit down, you realize this is more than just a pretty face. Height adjustable arms only add to the comfort story offered by this chair.
